    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是GradeSync。那异常分级怎么设计？我想到两种分支：Minor Issue触发警告状态，Major Issue直接进入Critical_State。这样分层合理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
