      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Minor Issue先到Warning_State，运维可以介入恢复；Major Issue直接进Critical_State，需要更激进的处置。另外Warning_State也可能升级，如果问题恶化要有Escalation到Critical_State的路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Warning_State",
        "Critical_State",
        "Escalation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：Normal_Operation分出两条线，一条到Warning_State标Minor Issue，一条到Critical_State标Major Issue。然后Warning_State回Normal_Operation标Resolved，再加一条Escalation到Critical_State。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Normal_Operation",
        "Warning_State",
        "Critical_State",
        "Resolved",
        "Escalation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Critical_State后面要分两种终局：如果问题无法解决，走Emergency_Landing回滚到GradeSync初始状态；如果可以修复并返回，走RTB回到Education_LMS_Portal。这两个终点不一样，一个是重启，一个是恢复服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Critical_State",
        "Emergency_Landing",
