      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Emergency_Landing是Cannot Resolve的极端情况，RTB是Can Return的恢复路径？然后Emergency_Landing回到GradeSync，RTB回到LMS Portal？",
      "elements_involved": [
